# Custom hydrators for derived applications
#
# This directory is for hydrators specific to your derived application.
# Files here should never exist in the base bioloop repository.
#
# To add a custom hydrator:
# 1. Create a new file (e.g., project.js)
# 2. Extend PrismaHydrate or Hydrate base class
# 3. Register virtual attributes if needed
# 4. Export the hydrator instance
# 5. Register it in ../index.js hydratorRegistry
#
# See ../custom/README.md for examples and guidelines
